job.title: HPSSC Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 379 Vacancies in Himachal Pradesh
job.body:
Total Vacancies:379

Name of the post:

  • Staff Nurse, Pharmacist, Jr Fireman, Office Assistant, Clerk, Steno Typist, Jr Engineer (Electrical, Civil) 

Description:

The Himachal Pradesh Staff Selection Commission issued a total of 379 vacancies in Himachal Pradesh shown above. The online application for these posts under HPSSC  shall start from 10-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 09-05-2021 till 11:59 PM. Further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these vacancies in Himachal Pradesh is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for HPSSC Various Vacancy Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the General/ E.W.S., Ex Servicemen is Rs. 360/-
  • The application fee for General IRDP, PH, Ward of Freedom Fighter is Rs. 120/-
  • For SC/ ST/ OBC/ BPL/ EWS (BPL) of HP: Rs. 120/-
  • For Ex Serviceman & Female candidates of HP: Nil

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 10-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 20-05-2021 till 11:59 PM

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 45 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

HPSSC various vacancy Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of HPSSC Various Vacancy is Rs. 14,000-35,000/month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies with educational qualification:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that HPSSC issued this notification for which vacancies.

 

How to apply for HPSSC Various Vacancy Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of HPSSC .
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of HPSSC Various Vacancy.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.

How to prepare for HPSSC exam?

Try this strategy to crack any exam:

  • You must have the syllabus.
  • Give a brief reading of the syllabus.
  • Buy a previous year's papers book.
  • See the most frequent topics that came in previous papers.
  • First, finish them and revise them on daily basis.
  • Recommended books to crack this exam.
  • The final and most important steps are to revise, revise and revise.
